snippet.title: Forza Horizon 4 Hot Wheels™ Legends Car Pack
snippet.description:
The Hot Wheels Legends Car Pack contains six custom built cars featured in the international Hot Wheels™ Legends Tour, where they competed for the chance to become iconic 1:64 scale Hot Wheels™ die-cast toys. Now you can experience these uniquely designed machines in Forza Horizon 4. Available February 22nd.  

https://www.xbox.com/games/forza-horizon-4

AUDIO DESCRIPTION: https://youtu.be/nh5_fx2auUw
